ass=\\\"foreign text-wy\\\" lang=\\\"bo-LATN\\\"\u003eyid dga’\u003c/em\u003e). (2) A mountain in the eastern sea between \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9338\\\"\u003eJambudvīpa\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9847\\\"\u003eVideha\u003c/span\u003e (\u003cem class=\\\"foreign text-wy\\\" lang=\\\"bo-LATN\\\"\u003eyid bde ba\u003c/em\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Happy Mind\",\"tibetan\":\"ཡིད་དགའ།, ཡིད་བདེ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"yid bde ba, yid dga’\"}},{\"uuid\":\"d4cd314d-1814-4c28-bbeb-799d1d6e6435\",\"authority\":\"1cf33d9a-c311-4205-a121-4fbffa9bdff1\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of sixteen realms that surround the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9630\\\"\u003eReviving Hell\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Harmed by Pain\",\"tibetan\":\"སྡུག་བསྔལ་གྱིས་གནོད་པ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"duḥkhataḍāga\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"sdug bsngal gyis gnod pa\"}},{\"uuid\":\"3726be32-a663-4eef-bf46-ff0252c07e0a\",\"authority\":\"0905550c-0e26-4280-b6e6-dc5e7b59c867\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA town in \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9847\\\"\u003eVideha\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Harmful Forest\",\"tibetan\":\"གནོད་པའི་ནགས།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"gnod pa’i nags\"}},{\"uuid\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"authority\":\"7c963930-ded9-4485-b0dd-8d2d3f0c52f6\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eThe third among the four verbal misdeeds.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"harsh words\",\"tibetan\":\"ཚིག་རྩུབ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"pāruṣya\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"tshig rtsub\"}},{\"uuid\":\"c9f11341-559b-494a-8878-0248ae23ef8d\",\"authority\":\"13fcc2a1-ffd3-4762-919a-83d301dc82ff\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA mountain in \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9417\\\"\u003eLiving on the Peak\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Heap in the Stream\",\"tibetan\":\"ཀླུང་ན་བརྩེགས་པ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"klung na brtsegs pa\"}},{\"uuid\":\"60f195d8-5e68-4c45-ad04-fc5bff26712d\",\"authority\":\"22172cca-b955-402f-98b3-ea098705dc2e\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA peak upon Mount \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9739\\\"\u003eSumeru\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Heap of Incense\",\"tibetan\":\"སྤོས་བརྩེགས།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"spos brtsegs\"}},{\"uuid\":\"ab1dc604-693c-4013-9047-1f9f17f7b945\",\"authority\":\"e6246750-6aaa-4a6e-b228-a0c890e18faa\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA mountain off \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9847\\\"\u003eVideha\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Heap of Iron\",\"tibetan\":\"ལྕགས་ཀྱི་ཕུང་པོ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"lcags kyi phung po\"}},{\"uuid\":\"ec2af397-5749-42d6-8613-53aeadf43ef5\",\"authority\":\"186761e4-6ecd-4d06-bb13-312ee2960fc6\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of sixteen realms that surround the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8975\\\"\u003eCrushing Hell\u003c/span\u003e. Alternatively referred to as \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9468\\\"\u003eMetallic Fire\u003c/span\u003e (\u003cem class=\\\"foreign text-wy\\\" lang=\\\"bo-LATN\\\"\u003elcags kyi me\u003c/em\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Heap of Live Coals of Iron-dust\",\"tibetan\":\"ལྕགས་ཀྱི་ཕྱེ་མ་མེ་མདག་གི་ར་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"ayaś­cūrṇāṅgāra­nikara\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"lcags kyi phye ma me mdag gi ra ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"e19490fe-96ef-407f-8605-6b8e15d6c0fb\",\"authority\":\"8b010532-761a-4dfd-90a4-1f1dc2c82dda\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA lake on the mountain called “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9085\\\"\u003eExcellence of Exquisite Intelligence\u003c/span\u003e.”\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Heaps of Fresh Butter\",\"tibetan\":\"མར་སར་གྱི་གོང་བུ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"mar sar gyi gong bu\"}},{\"uuid\":\"5a90184b-4c5f-424b-8a34-4d859dc83b2f\",\"authority\":\"b662e79b-4cff-4567-b74a-1c23d3f1fea7\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eThe term is most simply interpreted as “those who hear” the Buddha’s teaching, i.e. his disciples, but the additional \u003cspan class=\\\"ignore\\\"\u003eelement\u003c/span\u003e that they then “make it heard” to others is often present in canonical glosses. In a Mahāyāna context it refers to those disciples of the Buddha who aspire to attain the state of a \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8627\\\"\u003eworthy one\u003c/span\u003e (\u003cem class=\\\"foreign break text-sa\\\" lang=\\\"sa-LATN\\\"\u003earhat\u003c/em\u003e), and not to embark on the path of a bodhisattva (with buddhahood as its ultimate goal).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"hearer\",\"tibetan\":\"ཉན་ཐོས།\",\"sanskrit\":\"śrāvaka\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"nyan thos\"}},{\"uuid\":\"7914a74a-dcb8-4c66-80f4-6948756ba88a\",\"authority\":\"0e54ff2f-2403-45cb-9d3f-3d504edbe336\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm that neighbors the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9278\\\"\u003eHell of Intense Heat\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Heartbreaking Cries\",\"tibetan\":\"སྙིང་རྗེ་རྗེ་སྐད་སྒྲ་འབྱིན་པ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"karuṇānināda\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"snying rje rje skad sgra ’byin pa\"}},{\"uuid\":\"01cf2171-1722-4bd1-be63-0cf55b101a24\",\"authority\":\"e4cadcd3-4e09-43c9-9bc0-00b3e45ae505\",\"