3eHeaven Free from Strife\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving in the Stream\",\"tibetan\":\"རྒྱུན་གྱི་གནས་ན་རྣམ་པར་རྒྱུ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rgyun gyi gnas na rnam par rgyu ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"71d882ef-cdb8-4fc9-a848-74daf9e05d86\",\"authority\":\"b415aa77-a0a8-4d67-895f-b607e10a7188\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm in the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9276\\\"\u003eHeaven of the Thirty-Three\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving in the Wink of an Eye\",\"tibetan\":\"མིག་ཕྱེ་ཞིང་འགྲོ་བ་བཙུམས་ནས་འགྲོ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"nimeṣonmeṣa­gatī\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"mig phye zhing ’gro ba btsums nas ’gro ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"e7d0d16d-942c-4c23-8c14-8c9e0c159ebf\",\"authority\":\"7d008cf5-98d1-4d39-940d-59127a7efb76\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of the twenty-seven realms of the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9266\\\"\u003eHeaven Free from Strife\u003c/span\u003e, presumably the same as \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9506\\\"\u003eMoving in Mixed Environments\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving in Vast Environments\",\"tibetan\":\"རྒྱ་ཆེན་པོའི་ཁོར་ཡུག་ན་རྒྱུ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rgya chen po’i khor yug na rgyu ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"6305dfbd-1e36-4cbb-ac0c-6569790502c8\",\"authority\":\"a6f3f064-c032-4bb1-b154-9bf160fa6ad6\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm in the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9276\\\"\u003eHeaven of the Thirty-Three\u003c/span\u003e. Also called \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9627\\\"\u003eResembling the Full Moon\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving Like the Moon\",\"tibetan\":\"ཟླ་བའི་གནས་ལྟར་རྒྱུ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"candrāyaṇacāra\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"zla ba’i gnas ltar rgyu ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"348382dc-3074-4fb3-a514-f23a378782ec\",\"authority\":\"f7bd4f4f-b35a-4400-bacd-92aaabee0763\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm inhabited by \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8530\\\"\u003egarland-bearer gods\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving Mind\",\"tibetan\":\"ཡིད་གཡོ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"yid g.yo ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"c02e9815-604b-4dc5-a8ee-29a1fabd385e\",\"authority\":\"714f274d-e19a-49ef-98dc-834a3abd3a88\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA river on \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9657\\\"\u003eSaṅkāśa\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving Moon\",\"tibetan\":\"ཟླ་བ་རྒྱུ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"zla ba rgyu ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"3dc335b1-19ac-4b70-b968-99d8515d89c8\",\"authority\":\"5e7b5388-7209-4196-9b2d-39e3f1a6aaba\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm in the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9276\\\"\u003eHeaven of the Thirty-Three\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Moving on Springy Ground\",\"tibetan\":\"དམའ་བ་དང་མཐོ་བ་ན་རྒྱུ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"nimnonnatā­cāriṇī\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"dma’ ba dang mtho ba na rgyu ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"59acec3a-ea32-4a6e-9148-58f4a051988f\",\"authority\":\"c1c54859-2ee0-4a54-9365-8124192b2806\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA class of \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8622\\\"\u003evidyādharas\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"moving without delay\",\"tibetan\":\"འགོར་བ་མེད་པར་འགྲོ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"’gor ba med par ’gro ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"47f6a541-68e6-42f1-b856-15dde9d7fa25\",\"authority\":\"9c0656c3-a09e-4a3f-9cf8-e549f52e4d8d\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA mountain on the continent of \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9398\\\"\u003eKuru\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Multicolor\",\"tibetan\":\"འདྲེས་པ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"’dres pa\"}},{\"uuid\":\"8b6f4a70-ae8d-47c6-a7c7-8d7c250bda4c\",\"authority\":\"d40eaf0e-5fdb-47a7-8ae9-e10103db5de9\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eMusāragalva is fossilized coral that has undergone transformation under millions of years of underwater pressure. It appears in one version of the list of seven precious materials. The Tibetan tradition describes it as being formed from ice over a long period of time. It can also refer to tridacna (\u003cem class=\\\"foreign\\\"\u003eTridacnidae\u003c/em\u003e) shell, which is also presently referred to by the name musaragalva. Attempts to identify musāragalva have included sapphire, cat’s eye, red coral, conch, and amber.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"musāragalva\",\"tibetan\":\"མུ་ས་ར།, མུ་སཱ་ར་གལ་བ།, མུ་སཱ་ར་གལྦ།, སྤུག\",\"sanskrit\":\"musāragalva\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"mu sA ra gal ba, mu sA ra gal+ba, mu sa ra, spug\"}},{\"uuid\":\"b6357997-e45e-4bbe-bc0c-0c16104deb5f\",\"authority\":\"fd53dea9-1578-4bb4-be17-08350ddecd7f\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eKing of the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8531\\\"\u003egods\u003c/span\u003e in the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9266\\\"\u003eHeaven Free from Strife\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Musulundha\",\"tibetan\":\"མུ་སུ་ལུན་དྷ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"musulundha\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"mu su lun dha\"}},{\"uuid\":\"a38ef4c0-9af9-4971-b8fb-4159020f9cbd\",\"authority\":\"0ee021d3-783a-4c43-96f3-81dc0c463fb5\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003e(1) One of sixteen realms that surround the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9235\\\"\u003eGreat Howling Hell\u003c/span\u003e. (2) One of sixteen realms that surround the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9630\\\"\u003eReviving Hell\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Mutation\",\"tibetan\":\"གཞན་དུ་འགྱུར་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"anyathā­parivarta\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"gzhan du ’gyur ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"245442f8-7254-4beb-aa77-7e8c8c49aaa7\",\"authority\":\"c6db0b6d-7d7b-42e9-84a5-7b41f56d9518\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of sixteen realms that surround the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9630\\\"\u003eReviving Hell\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Mutilation by Iron\",\"tibetan\":\"ལྕགས་ཀྱིས་བསྒྱུར་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"ayaḥ­parivartaka\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"lcags kyis bsgyur ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"ef01787d-7848-4ab7-9912-d6f0e9b2e79a\",\"authority\":\"5543b873-8dd9-4e80-8306-b4366f10f6a9\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of sixteen realms that surround the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9235\\\"\u003eGreat Howling Hell\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Mutual Harm\",\"tibetan\":\"ཕན་ཚུན་གནོད་པ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"paraspara­pīḍā­saṃvarta\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"phan tshun gnod pa\"}},{\"uuid\":\"67f3257e-94a4-43ae-95ea-77377a4d92b8\",\"authority\":\"8467fa02-e5e0-4b9e-b79c-9abd4ca1c2a1\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm of the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8617\\\"\u003etriple-lute-bearer gods\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Mutual Liking\",\"tibetan\":\"ཕན་ཚུན་དགའ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"phan tshun dga’\"}},{\"uuid\":\"90cb0864-69bd-4721-b137-0150b05ab596\",\"authority\":\"c40f7f48-3f84-44d6-bcd3-e3d193148554\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA moun