e\":\"yongs ’du\"}},{\"uuid\":\"f29dcd91-297e-4887-aa58-3183241cf3e6\",\"authority\":\"c8366dca-b2a2-4eda-b772-f7a4c0d2aa0b\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA mountain range. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003e(We have been unable to identify this mountain, or mountain range. However, since \u003cem class=\\\"foreign break text-sa\\\" lang=\\\"sa-LATN\\\"\u003eyongs ’du\u003c/em\u003e is a translation of “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9551\\\"\u003epārijāta\u003c/span\u003e tree,” we have opted for this translation. Perhaps it refers to the mountains where the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9551\\\"\u003epārijāta\u003c/span\u003e tree grows?)\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Pārijāta Mountains\",\"tibetan\":\"རི་ཡོངས་འདུ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"pārijāta\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"ri yongs ’du\"}},{\"uuid\":\"a80ab03a-4f55-422a-a81c-3a1777991822\",\"authority\":\"21533ad4-7c2b-4e60-b015-b8d7f89ca82f\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA park in \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8820\\\"\u003eAttached to That\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Park of Golden Shade\",\"tibetan\":\"གསེར་གྱི་གྲིབ་མའི་ཚལ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"gser gyi grib ma’i tshal\"}},{\"uuid\":\"46f5d233-5510-4509-8fa5-98b26ccd7350\",\"authority\":\"04aaa2ef-2493-4132-9d59-9fc87480b26d\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of four parks that surround the city of \u003cspan data-ref=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9605\\\"\u003e\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9605\\\"\u003eRadiant\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Park of Passion\",\"tibetan\":\"རྒྱགས་པའི་ཀུན་དགའ་ར་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rgyags pa’i kun dga’ ra ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"22005d0f-ea22-4b04-800a-c38653ae314f\",\"authority\":\"ca9a017c-bc00-4