realm in the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9276\\\"\u003eHeaven of the Thirty-Three\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Supreme Splendor\",\"tibetan\":\"གཟི་བརྗིད་མཆོག\",\"sanskrit\":\"tejomukha\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"gzi brjid mchog\"}},{\"uuid\":\"276335c0-277e-446a-a194-071c8f1fc1d0\",\"authority\":\"4b7ed3b8-888c-4fe3-9eba-158a027fd12d\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne of the twenty-seven realms of the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9266\\\"\u003eHeaven Free from Strife\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Supreme Strength\",\"tibetan\":\"རབ་ཀྱི་ཤུགས་ཀྱི་བདག, རབ་ཀྱི་ཤུགས།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"rab kyi shugs, rab kyi shugs kyi bdag\"}},{\"uuid\":\"3486e635-0221-48dd-999d-dc34168f9c40\",\"authority\":\"fad69ed5-6842-4dcf-a522-8cfe97fbd067\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA river on \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9657\\\"\u003eSaṅkāśa\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Surrounded by Nakra Crocodiles\",\"tibetan\":\"ཆུ་སྲིན་ན་ཀྲས་བསྐོར་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"chu srin na kras bskor ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"2e95ec85-ff97-429c-b743-0776a9a5d3c0\",\"authority\":\"a4e5f80d-16d9-4ae8-a689-fd6cdde70c14\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA river on \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9657\\\"\u003eSaṅkāśa\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Surrounded by Nyaronya\",\"tibetan\":\"ཉ་རོ་ཧི་འཁོར་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"nya ro hi ’khor ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"e7bb511d-8964-4f44-ba8a-859bc3039c59\",\"authority\":\"f9c21ed2-adfa-4f04-8f0a-0f8fe68fc540\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA mountain in the sea west of \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9338\\\"\u003eJambudvīpa\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Suśīmo\",\"tibetan\":\"སུ་ཤཱི་མོ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"suśīmo\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"su shI mo\"}},{\"uuid\":\"1d039d99-48ab-4d08-8328-d5981259cd9a\",\"authority\":\"d4d6ec40-f9f0-49e3-a1c9-9255b155b680\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA realm inhabited by \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-8530\\\"\u003egarland-bearer gods\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Sustained by Fruition\",\"tibetan\":\"འབྲས་བུས་ཉེ་བར་འཚོ་བ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"’bras bus nye bar ’tsho ba\"}},{\"uuid\":\"26d538b0-50c4-41e6-ae57-cd785d47ba44\",\"authority\":\"2b8ba405-8b7b-42b6-9571-c4a7067eaa0b\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA grove in \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9820\\\"\u003eUnmixed\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Sustained by the Finest Tastes\",\"tibetan\":\"རོ་བརྒྱ་མཆོག་གིས་བསྟེན་པ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"ro brgya mchog gis bsten pa\"}},{\"uuid\":\"9e0171e8-23fa-46cb-8835-a71798ac4b91\",\"authority\":\"d471865c-de07-420e-914f-0a8fd73445e0\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA land to the north of \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9338\\\"\u003eJambudvīpa\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Susthali\",\"tibetan\":\"སུས་ཐ་ལི།\",\"sanskrit\":\"susthali\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"sus tha li\"}},{\"uuid\":\"643935d0-63fb-47fc-8abc-2bc1b02a1331\",\"authority\":\"73789e6d-8b90-414f-ab00-df45bd1a7268\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eIn Buddhism it refers to the Buddha’s teachings, whatever their length, and in terms of the three divisions of the Buddha’s teachings, it is the category of teachings other than those on the \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9974\\\"\u003eVinaya\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9985\\\"\u003eAbhidharma\u003c/span\u003e. It is also used as a category to contrast with the tantra teachings. Another very specific meaning is when it is classed as one of the nine or twelve aspects of the Dharma. In that context \u003cem class=\\\"foreign break text-sa\\\" lang=\\\"sa-LATN\\\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\\\"ignore\\\"\u003esūtra\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/em\u003e means “discourse.”\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Sūtra\",\"tibetan\":\"མདོ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"sūtra\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"mdo\"}},{\"uuid\":\"b04744cc-c072-44a3-813e-4300a50532da\",\"authority\":\"acc001e9-e025-45ec-ba7e-b1400c2d26b4\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eOne among the twelve sections of scripture. See also entry on the term “\u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9986\\\"\u003esūtra\u003c/span\u003e.“\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"sūtras\",\"tibetan\":\"མདོའི་སྡེ།\",\"sanskrit\":\"sūtra\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"mdo’i sde\"}},{\"uuid\":\"360ac958-8bd5-478a-a636-bf6febad0963\",\"authority\":\"526587de-2165-43b1-8bf6-b7083e375280\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA region of Southeast Asia visited by Indians.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Suvarṇadvīpa\",\"tibetan\":\"གསེར་གླིང་།\",\"sanskrit\":\"suvarṇadvīpa\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"gser gling\"}},{\"uuid\":\"913084ba-555f-4dd5-941a-b37d80557442\",\"authority\":\"6434a3c8-9858-499b-b3a7-9a7bfe5563fc\",\"definition\":\"\u003cp class=\\\"definition\\\"\u003eA forest on \u003cspan data-glossary-id=\\\"UT22084-068-021-9241\\\"\u003eGreat Slope\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"names\":{\"english\":\"Suvelang Forest\",\"tibetan\":\"སུ་བེ་ལང་གི་ནགས།\",\"sanskrit\":\"\",\"pali\":\"\",\"chinese\":\"\",\"wylie\":\"su be lang gi nags\"}},{\"uuid\":\"27fc3666-d4c8-49c1-b53f-a8500096d0d3\",\"authority\":\"7227b93f-6c2c-4b7e-ac19-755c5b13888b\",\"definition\":\"\u