ss="pt-1"><span class="font-tibetan text-base">རྨ་བྱའི་ཚོགས།</span></li></ul><div class="glossary-instance-definition"><p class="definition">A mountain on <span data-glossary-id="UT22084-068-021-9847">Videha</span>.</p></div></div></div></div><div id="0710916c-4145-4750-8f62-2a9e8e5796ce" class="relative scroll-mt-20"><button type="button" id="radix-_R_jjl5anpftt6btb_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="absolute labeled -left-16 w-16 text-end hover:cursor-pointer whitespace-pre-line leading-4">g.462</button><div class="passage pl-6 @c/sidebar:pl-4"><div class="flex gap-1 flex-col p-0 @c/sidebar:-mt-0.5"><div class="text-secondary font-sans text-base font-bold">Flow</div><ul class="ml-4 list-disc"><li class="italic">rnam par ’bab pa</li><li class="pt-1"><span class="font-tibetan text-base">རྣམ་པར་འབབ་པ།</span></li></ul><div class="glossary-instance-definition"><p class="definition">A forest on <span data-glossary-id="UT22084-068-021-9657">Saṅkāśa</span>.</p></div></div></div></div><div id="a1548279-220d-4a61-88f0-dcfcc0cab9f4" class="relative scroll-mt-20"><button type="button" id="radix-_R_jjt5anpftt6btb_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="absolute labeled -left-16 w-16 text-end hover:cursor-pointer whitespace-pre-line leading-4">g.463</button><div class="passage pl-6 @c/sidebar:pl-4"><div class="flex gap-1 flex-col p-0 @c/sidebar:-mt-0.5"><div class="text-secondary font-sans text-base font-bold">Flow of a Hundred Lakes</div><ul class="ml-4 list-disc"><li class="italic">mtsho brgya rab tu ’bab pa</li><li class="pt-1"><span class="font-tibetan text-base">མཚོ་བརྒྱ་རབ་ཏུ་འབབ་པ།</span></li></ul><div class="glossary-instance-definition"><p class="definition">A part of <span data-glossary-id="UT22084-068-021-9495">Mountainous Garland</span>.</p></div></div></div></div><div id="23c2946f-519d-4081-a4bf-56502fa63bd3" class="relative scroll-mt-20"><button type="button" id="radix-_R_jk55anpftt6btb_" aria-ha