trs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":381,\"uuid\":\"810dfccc-571b-43a3-a716-89344f5bdd81\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Moreover, when one contemplates the very subtle aspects of the ten unvirtuous actions in other ways, one will understand how they lead sentient beings to roam through the realms of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":182}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":182,\"end\":193},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"2fec422b-450c-4f2e-a6c3-4f0cbf597a72\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":193,\"end\":195}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirits\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":195,\"end\":211},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"bd2c0ad6-2c28-49d8-abdf-b48127e44476\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":211,\"end\":217}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animals\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":217,\"end\":224},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"a26872a4-3a5a-4042-bf81-377e149d72f2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena perceive this either through knowledge derived from hearing or by seeing with the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":224,\"end\":370}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":370,\"end\":380},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"0473443a-f039-4743-82c8-1d3f620e38a5\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":380,\"end\":381}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"d21dfa53-d08c-44c9-a025-eced409216d1\",\"sort\":1188,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.34\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":107,\"uuid\":\"d581ca01-656a-45f4-8904-8a96a37df093\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"a6a1341e-2c71-4b6f-9a71-caa06257a3ba\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“In this regard, you may wonder how one may resort to, become habituated to, and increase acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":98}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":98,\"end\":105},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"c86cde53-345a-444c-b2a6-81da248a7f55\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":105,\"end\":107}}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":107,\"end\":1514,\"uuid\":\"12e0f02a-0615-4d9b-a09d-1cf9fb0a7d42\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Regarding the first of these, one may associate with negative companions, students, or friends who kill. One may enjoy their company, fool around with them, work with them, and stay with them. One may find such people trustworthy and in possession of good qualities, and thus adopt their behavior. Unvirtuous teachers and students who have the habit of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":107,\"end\":461}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":461,\"end\":468},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"75abaeec-fedc-4927-9945-3fa29a561d89\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" people will tell all sorts of stories to justify \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":468,\"end\":518}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":518,\"end\":525},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"75e95fc4-0e3f-4ec3-a194-b17ff8716a38\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". These are not the path and only lead others to indulge in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":525,\"end\":585}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":585,\"end\":592},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"2c03a421-d25f-4b87-ae0a-935fc03e1a88\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". In this manner, they may tell stories about sacrificial offerings, stories about wild game, or wicked stories based on their gustatory cravings. Similarly, they may tell stories about retaliation against hostile adversaries or relations, or stories based on their craving for these people’s belongings. Similarly, taking great in delight in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":592,\"end\":935}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"affliction\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":935,\"end\":945},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9a4b2555-d9c2-41b4-a5c0-2a8a0a115fa5\",\"uuid\":\"9b74bc42-5329-4f39-94da-4fa22cc63e62\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", they will tell stories based on their craving for material things or about deeds for acquiring fame. In these ways, they lead others on. If one trusts and adheres to such people, one may also end up resorting to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":945,\"end\":1159}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1159,\"end\":1166},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"64d0e66e-110e-4798-a8ba-8565d38a67d5\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Resorting to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1166,\"end\":1181}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1181,\"end\":1188},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"749b786a-e08a-4b26-a3a5-b6fa8a324c91\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" results in entering the realms of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1188,\"end\":1223}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1223,\"end\":1234},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"49df8e77-a27b-4a29-976e-87261cabaae9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1234,\"end\":1236}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirits\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1236,\"end\":1252},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"c78b75ef-08d1-4af8-af83-b3985a0421e3\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1252,\"end\":1258}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animals\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1258,\"end\":1265},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"390ee3c1-bece-490a-9507-7f6cb5ddf21c\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Such effects are unattractive, ugly, and unpleasant, and are condemned by all wise people. Even if one is born human, one’s life will be short. Thus, the taking of life stemming from a wicked teacher makes one become totally habituated to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1265,\"end\":1506}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1506,\"end\":1513},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"b1d93d53-e0de-4530-acef-e2aade593e0b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1513,\"end\":1514}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"2a5034cd-4fd4-4db5-a91b-7fd5a53ecf05\",\"sort\":1215,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.35\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":687,\"uuid\":\"2a5034cd-4fd4-4db5-a91b-7fd5a53ecf05\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What does it mean to become habituated to unwholesome people? Based on the taking of life that is influenced by unwholesome people as just described, one rejoices in, appreciates, contemplates, and condones acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":216}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":216,\"end\":223},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"9e483860-8d89-4cce-9ae2-44a9edacc067\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Setting one’s mind on \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":223,\"end\":247}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":247,\"end\":254},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"cc697bd6-bfda-401d-a733-678aa5820a50\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", one succeeds in slaying others by numerous means. Without counting it as a fault and condemning it, one delights in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":254,\"end\":372}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":372,\"end\":379},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"9eb9dad5-2e17-4e79-acb1-c7179aefc69f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and does not refrain from it. In this way, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":379,\"end\":423}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":423,\"end\":430},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"f367e112-4ef0-4d2a-aad2-3f82b736f80f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" becomes second nature. Those who otherwise have the habit of not \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":430,\"end\":496}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":496,\"end\":503},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"19c1378d-54da-4d68-aa80-8dade4000625\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will be drawn into the practice of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":503,\"end\":539}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":539,\"end\":546},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"c2f272a8-dfcd-4c2a-a0a4-3c0b5c7b54fd\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". One will also engage in the kinds of conversation, and so on, alluded to previously. This is what it is like to grow habituated to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":546,\"end\":679}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":679,\"end\":686},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"60a18ce6-dbbf-4620-85c7-b5b6c8bd885e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":686,\"end\":687}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"109a6102-cd7c-4067-892d-8dde0936e236\",\"sort\":1232,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.36\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":498,\"uuid\":\"109a6102-cd7c-4067-892d-8dde0936e236\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What does it mean to increase \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":31}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":31,\"end\":38},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"d25f1291-2029-4b54-953c-dd013bb59cb1\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Once habituated to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":38,\"end\":59}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":59,\"end\":66},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"ecc4b9cb-6b21-4c31-bf40-581933eea504\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" in the way just described, one may associate with evil companions and thereby greatly expand one’s murderous activities. Thus, one may craft poisonous arrows, gather dogs and raptors, and accept the protection of barbarous people. Fond of warfare, one may wear chain mail, weapons, swords, lances, axes, disks, helmets, and so on‍—thus adopting all possible instruments for killing others. Such is the person who increases \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":66,\"end\":490}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":490,\"end\":497},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"f6d7aa83-4a2e-427f-96f4-9a35f4d879f2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":497,\"end\":498}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"99d9fb7a-4a7b-441e-80d1-9bf19b0ece98\",\"sort\":1242,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.37\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":313,\"uuid\":\"99d9fb7a-4a7b-441e-80d1-9bf19b0ece98\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Through such causes, bases, and conditions one will be born in the realms of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":78}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":78,\"end\":89},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"e504a52d-8e16-4903-b685-d5b9535b2670\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":89,\"end\":91}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animals\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":91,\"end\":98},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"b19a1065-f532-474a-91ee-9d7eb5aacf84\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":98,\"end\":104}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirits\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":104,\"end\":120},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"9c725ca7-5b36-41f4-aa4b-9a8411ea114e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and so be tormented by unbearable harm. Based on whether one’s \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":120,\"end\":185}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":185,\"end\":192},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"a9e31be9-da5a-4dd1-95bd-e3ee556a3acd\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" was minor, intermediate, or severe, there will be a corresponding experience of minor, intermediate, or severe \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":192,\"end\":304}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ripening\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":304,\"end\":312},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e6c5ad9a-9509-4706-9d6f-5fad607030a7\",\"uuid\":\"ff48039c-2454-495b-bf26-052c916ee3ac\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":312,\"end\":313}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"5276180c-af4a-434d-a2d2-6f4ba994be84\",\"sort\":1256,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.38\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":373,\"uuid\":\"5276180c-af4a-434d-a2d2-6f4ba994be84\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Whenever an act has been carried out and accumulated it will also ripen. Therefore, acts that were done by oneself will also be experienced by oneself. Hence, if one has become disenchanted with \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":196}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":196,\"end\":212},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"1f5c6975-e5dc-48af-9a69-f5e1e6081f53\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" one should give up evil acts and pursue what is virtuous. These are the explanations of resorting to, becoming habituated to, and increasing the taking of life.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":212,\"end\":373}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"121c2387-949e-4f0d-bb23-eb18c00578df\",\"sort\":1260,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.39\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":190,\"uuid\":\"bbfdac3d-30a5-4e00-97c1-227359bdcb39\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"976bb7a9-4366-479b-b9c6-c80515f1cd55\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“How does one resort to, become habituated to, and increase acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":68}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":68,\"end\":76},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"62e41a67-aa8a-4963-8ccb-8c566497324c\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? How does resorting to, becoming habituated to, and increasing such acts lead to the experience of life in hell? \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":76,\"end\":190}}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":190,\"end\":1377,\"uuid\":\"01748c3a-1710-4568-b752-7fdde21bacc3\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“People whose discipline has degenerated will naturally be disposed to thievery. When they associate with negative companions or students they will engage in minor, intermediate, or great acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":190,\"end\":386}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":386,\"end\":394},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"820887b1-5d2b-4f75-8f40-0c503d944b56\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Minor acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":394,\"end\":410}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":410,\"end\":418},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"4955d504-df1a-49eb-a4f0-206efd2aae70\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" occur as described earlier, when one takes others’ possessions out of fear of otherwise being punished by the authorities. Intermediate acts occur when one steals smaller things as long as one does not steal from a field of excellence. Even if a minor thing is taken from the Buddha, Dharma, or Saṅgha, the result will be great. However, if one has improperly taken from the Buddha, Dharma, or Saṅgha but later makes proportionate offerings to them, the negative act can be purified, especially in the case of the Buddha and the Dharma. If one steals from the saṅgha, it cannot be purified without experiencing some painful effects because the saṅgha is a field with a particularly strong karmic charge. If one steals a means of sustenance from the congregation one will fall into the great hells. If one steals something else from the congregation, one will instead be born in one of the hells that surround that of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":418,\"end\":1336}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ultimate Torment\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1336,\"end\":1352},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8f5efab1-1d55-410b-b89a-af49ca7d6f7d\",\"uuid\":\"ec1ed26c-5f89-43ee-819a-a295e97a3536\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", such as \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1352,\"end\":1362}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great Darkness\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1362,\"end\":1376},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"812114f7-78e5-4500-bc9f-6c772e79b1c0\",\"uuid\":\"403db475-9621-40ce-807a-a368b19ab216\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1376,\"end\":1377},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"93093afa-feaa-4fce-8fce-1fb3fa98b47f\",\"label\":\"18\",\"uuid\":\"188a3aec-74de-465b-900c-e4e9bf4311d8\",\"start\":1377,\"end\":1377,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"dcc90281-1aa0-4bb9-bc72-b02e72a066ea\",\"sort\":1276,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.40\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":313,\"uuid\":\"dcc90281-1aa0-4bb9-bc72-b02e72a066ea\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“If one takes up, resorts to, rejoices in, becomes habituated to, and increases \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":80}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":80,\"end\":88},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"d07d48a0-3538-4b57-afa4-901f1fbbad4c\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", even minor forms of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":88,\"end\":110}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":110,\"end\":118},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"f29651ba-8b10-4cd3-aad1-78b74986f667\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will lead to birth among \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":118,\"end\":144}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":144,\"end\":155},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"c487754c-a8da-47bc-830f-12148aebaf82\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":155,\"end\":157}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animals\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":157,\"end\":164},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"c79d5932-03b0-4515-b3c5-7406879b957c\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":164,\"end\":170}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirits\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":170,\"end\":186},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"ab848d2e-9b3e-437e-8afa-52d0b4cf1bdf\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". If one does not develop attachment to and rejoice in the act, and instead regrets it, the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":186,\"end\":278}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ripening\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":278,\"end\":286},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e6c5ad9a-9509-4706-9d6f-5fad607030a7\",\"uuid\":\"cd8310dc-c4fa-404c-aa24-857c83e679e4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will become indeterminate.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":286,\"end\":313}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"48ea29ec-6793-4a1a-a709-9545bd6914bc\",\"sort\":1290,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.41\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":130,\"uuid\":\"48ea29ec-6793-4a1a-a709-9545bd6914bc\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Resorting to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":14}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":14,\"end\":22},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"0215ffff-37c1-4ebd-b4e6-bd1e1912debc\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" occurs when someone who is inclined to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":22,\"end\":62}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"take what was not given\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":62,\"end\":85},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7169b9fd-d93b-43b7-af46-5708360b5712\",\"uuid\":\"37069c6b-920a-4395-999d-2391153d3555\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" engages in various ways in acts of thievery.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":85,\"end\":130}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"886c27c1-5c9c-46e5-974e-0e0c26a9c462\",\"sort\":1296,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.42\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":328,\"uuid\":\"886c27c1-5c9c-46e5-974e-0e0c26a9c462\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What is meant by becoming habituated to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":41}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":41,\"end\":49},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"d2fa5e97-31c7-4ffe-bec8-c4edd8079a8e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Having obtained something that was stolen, one may rejoice and delight in the robbers and thieves, and happily consume or employ what was stolen. Considering such conduct to be a good quality, one may encourage and help others to steal. This is becoming habituated to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":49,\"end\":319}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":319,\"end\":327},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"96766be8-88b5-4f3e-9b1f-841068dc52f2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":327,\"end\":328}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"a85c2cfd-6fe4-4728-ae86-0298b5aefb3b\",\"sort\":1302,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.43\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":615,\"uuid\":\"a85c2cfd-6fe4-4728-ae86-0298b5aefb3b\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“How is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":8}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":8,\"end\":16},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"5882a7df-44d8-4040-bd7f-942da57984df\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" increased? This occurs when one steals in order to enjoy linens, food, drink, clothing, jewelry, beverages, prostitutes, and ornaments. Delighted, one may think, ‘Among all pleasures, those which comes from \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":16,\"end\":224}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":224,\"end\":232},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"d03fce76-0bf4-4f4e-9ae8-ae796fdc8346\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" are the best!’ With such thoughts one enjoys linens, food, drink, clothing, jewelry, beverages, prostitutes, and ornaments. Thinking, ‘I must continue \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":232,\"end\":384}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":384,\"end\":392},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"632b1986-3e57-4b0e-a753-1c5c9d5d505a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" because it brings me so much pleasure,’ one then proceeds as described above. This is what it means to increase the act of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":392,\"end\":516}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":516,\"end\":524},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"b3a70d42-4a23-4801-9672-d26bf98215cd\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and as a result of that it is certain that sentient beings will experience life in a hell.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":524,\"end\":615}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"ef109669-90c5-4227-9582-308c4a5995ad\",\"sort\":1314,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.44\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":862,\"uuid\":\"ef109669-90c5-4227-9582-308c4a5995ad\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"6e52c2de-16de-464d-8541-9a6f76bf495c\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What does it mean to resort to, become habituated to, and increase acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":76}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":76,\"end\":93},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"3da6d99b-22f8-4f59-b072-167cc753e4a4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Overcome by an inappropriate mentality, one may become a type of being with a propensity for desire such as a swallow, duck, pheasant, parrot, peafowl, partridge, fish, or smoky creatures.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":93,\"end\":283},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"3f068d3f-0ed3-4d66-8c0d-3895011deaac\",\"label\":\"19\",\"uuid\":\"ed9640cf-4a6e-4b58-ad3d-4dbc55e688ee\",\"start\":283,\"end\":283,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" When such beings die and transfer out of the family of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":283,\"end\":339}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"asuras\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":339,\"end\":345},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5f1024e5-d735-4094-89c8-9a8baec55fd2\",\"uuid\":\"58b0534f-0007-4ee0-bd6a-f9588eb5847b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" they may be born among humans and associate with bad companions who are full of desire. With them they may then have inappropriate sexual relationships. Being mistaken in these two ways, they are filled with attachment, and they act in inappropriate ways to sate their insatiable desires. This makes it impossible for the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":345,\"end\":668}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"gandharvas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":668,\"end\":678},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b74ef150-7f77-412e-9bb2-1b4c5052267f\",\"uuid\":\"937e6bbd-327c-4c48-b7c2-672263368956\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", otherwise destined to be born there, to take birth, because it desecrates the birthplace. Such are the reasons why \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":678,\"end\":795}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":795,\"end\":812},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"6caa8ab2-4646-4f89-9c53-0927c7828f59\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", which is based on improper desire, is a misdeed.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":812,\"end\":862}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"69cc9272-069f-4118-8b24-9446aef9c891\",\"sort\":1326,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.45\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":996,\"uuid\":\"69cc9272-069f-4118-8b24-9446aef9c891\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Resorting to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":14}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":14,\"end\":31},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"ca7760bb-c11a-44fd-851b-f1eed281bb10\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" occurs when a person with an inordinate desire for carnal contact indulges in such acts and continuously repeats them, finding intense gratification in physical sensations. What does it mean to become habituated to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":31,\"end\":247}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":247,\"end\":264},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"82bd5141-e09b-4dcf-a96b-d8af883fa428\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? This refers to repeatedly engaging in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":264,\"end\":304}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":304,\"end\":321},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"32323e83-5c95-4ccc-bf2f-b23ae963ea46\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and thinking about it, becoming so infatuated with it that one gives up other pleasures only to focus on \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":321,\"end\":427}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":427,\"end\":444},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"6d6e9fb1-6bce-434e-823a-486cae6a00ad\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and the object of one’s desire. What is meant by increasing \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":444,\"end\":505}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":505,\"end\":522},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"4b8e9eda-c53f-4234-9ee4-056832805222\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Infantile, ordinary beings consumed by inappropriate mental activity feel that \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":522,\"end\":603}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":603,\"end\":620},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"f453f811-ff1b-4f0c-bc9e-5cfc1f9b905d\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is the best thing possible and they think that it is a mistake to classify such behavior as a form of misconduct. Instead they regard \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":620,\"end\":755}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":755,\"end\":772},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"45b0ee70-c0f8-4c62-9ff1-3ce68c57ca3b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" as a supreme quality and therefore encourage many others to engage in it. That is what it means to increase \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":772,\"end\":881}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":881,\"end\":898},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"00cb8e10-df40-4803-b1d2-b3478acb6753\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". These three physical misdeeds are unvirtuous actions in which infantile, ordinary beings engage.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":898,\"end\":996}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"554471c7-3731-4733-9966-88fc749af144\",\"sort\":1346,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.46\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":86,\"uuid\":\"dd2c03f6-dfe5-4bb2-af23-0bcfeee66be6\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"86503b69-b6e3-44c8-90bd-bb6fdb89eb9b\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What about the four verbal misdeeds: \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":38}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":38,\"end\":43},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"a071bff3-b8b7-4357-a4dc-eb9a1957347b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":43,\"end\":45}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":45,\"end\":58},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"e6f0bbe7-1484-486a-9408-c399441c21b7\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":58,\"end\":60}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":60,\"end\":71},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"ac0b4b0a-23d9-492a-8a47-6ef02fca1dad\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":71,\"end\":77}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"chatter\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":77,\"end\":84},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"aef12735-469a-4df0-8077-5d9f44c812e4\",\"uuid\":\"157fe6c4-7aa9-4779-befe-e5c390cdbb60\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":84,\"end\":86}}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":86,\"end\":705,\"uuid\":\"6357caa9-8671-41e7-bb89-1f68f48da8ba\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":86,\"end\":87}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":87,\"end\":92},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"2c2bf926-e4ae-4d30-97f2-23e3fa3ab3d7\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is to deceive oneself and others, for by speaking lies one does indeed deceive both oneself and others. There are five causes for \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":92,\"end\":223}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":223,\"end\":228},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"e08ddfb8-2dbd-4577-b85e-e0c033352269\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\": desire, anger, fear, personal gain, and indoctrination into the prescribed practices of a misguided religion. How does one lie? Whether at the royal court, in an assembly of householders, or among one’s relatives, one may lie to both those who are dear to oneself and those who are not. One may lie to those who are dear to oneself out of desire and to those who are not dear to oneself out of anger. One may also lie for the sake of personal gain and for the sake of wealth.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":228,\"end\":705}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"edf61a90-0774-4d0c-b32c-2a141493500e\",\"sort\":1363,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.47\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":667,\"uuid\":\"edf61a90-0774-4d0c-b32c-2a141493500e\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Moreover, indoctrination into the prescribed practices of a misguided religion is also a way of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":97}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":97,\"end\":102},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"fcd84b26-cf4a-41b0-9941-d1ca823d4089\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". For example, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":102,\"end\":117}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"brahmins\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":117,\"end\":125},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"d2beaf90-2596-4dcc-b765-8064c0cba1f3\",\"uuid\":\"8f8a6fed-802d-41c2-b0ee-f798430c13db\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" may declare that \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":125,\"end\":143}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":143,\"end\":148},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"fbca6537-33f4-49e8-871e-3a8a031a1c68\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will not carry any blemish as long as it is done to obtain desirable qualities, or to safeguard one’s wealth, protect one’s life, or obtain a bride. Such declarations are a form of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":148,\"end\":330}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":330,\"end\":335},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"131fe8dd-dd75-4216-a7b1-c683f79ef6cd\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" by means of indoctrination into the discipline of a misguided religion, and through such indoctrination into ignorant and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":335,\"end\":458}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"wrong views\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":458,\"end\":469},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5b457f37-2050-4b7a-a1bd-a4844678591e\",\"uuid\":\"b8d50cc6-ba8c-4de6-9986-9447a5039a88\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" one will come to live in an unbearable hell. Since \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":469,\"end\":521}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":521,\"end\":526},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"e5f59439-161e-40de-bf6d-26aadcaead72\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" plants the seeds of the hell realms it is best to entirely avoid any form of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":526,\"end\":604}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":604,\"end\":609},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"8d020716-8142-4737-8378-5644c8601872\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", even at the expense of one’s own life or that of others.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":609,\"end\":667}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"5bbc1d0e-01fa-4eaa-860d-f7048fd7e27e\",\"sort\":1379,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.48\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":177,\"uuid\":\"cbc71d1c-8126-4f29-9064-199d106b1639\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“One may also tell lies out of fear, as when someone thinks, ‘Unless I lie now, I may expose my life to serious danger for no reason.’ In such cases one lies motivated by fear. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":177}}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":177,\"end\":268,\"uuid\":\"1ca1f65c-c401-4e98-a260-cf30de6ba136\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Thus, these five factors cause infantile beings to lie. All of them are based on delusion.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":177,\"end\":268}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"36447035-5c2a-4400-b027-3910e860378e\",\"sort\":1382,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.49\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":39,\"uuid\":\"5ce0f046-e772-4c18-9797-6f9c3a56f46d\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"f008e12f-4143-41fb-ade2-2a72b7ee2dde\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“At this point, there are some verses: \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":39}}]},{\"type\":\"lineGroup\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":39,\"end\":169,\"uuid\":\"898cf18d-366c-4b66-9ccc-fda598191c94\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Disregarding what lies beyond this world \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":39,\"end\":81}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":39,\"end\":81,\"uuid\":\"f6c4bf63-bea6-407b-ba2d-a4af3ff6760d\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"And transgressing the one Dharma, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":81,\"end\":115}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":81,\"end\":115,\"uuid\":\"e7204c67-7480-4a1b-b65d-71ddbb8055ad\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Liars will not shy away \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":115,\"end\":139}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":115,\"end\":139,\"uuid\":\"6dc1d382-6b86-434a-97b4-04c696967bb3\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"From any form of negative act.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":139,\"end\":169}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":139,\"end\":169,\"uuid\":\"32051555-8cb7-47a6-b386-9f491d82648a\"}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"3a8c9f93-420b-4226-9429-905e76bbb5d7\",\"sort\":1391,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.50\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"lineGroup\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":150,\"uuid\":\"e5bb0781-f41a-44da-bcea-47e63bcc134b\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“As soon as they are born with a human body, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":45}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":45,\"uuid\":\"59c30e5a-534b-4956-9da0-4d2534039812\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Axe-like words will spout from their mouths. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":45,\"end\":90}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":45,\"end\":90,\"uuid\":\"e5ed7ef3-9673-4f07-acfa-8178bbd425c0\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"And thus, those who speak wrongly \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":90,\"end\":124}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":90,\"end\":124,\"uuid\":\"2d476e10-44cb-4b04-88de-af364ca0ed2c\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Only undermine themselves.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":124,\"end\":150}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":124,\"end\":150,\"uuid\":\"1478e948-b7f0-4030-bce1-764b82b642e5\"}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"c7176fb6-efe9-4297-b3be-4bda32f7b86d\",\"sort\":1399,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.51\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"lineGroup\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":182,\"uuid\":\"4214058c-0e67-4105-8ea0-7849237eabf8\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Speaking truthfully, not starting fights, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":43}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":43,\"uuid\":\"4f35e670-53a7-4428-934b-a524205869cc\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"And giving when asked, even if one has only a little‍— \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":43,\"end\":98}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":43,\"end\":98,\"uuid\":\"dddea0f2-55df-4a08-b1bc-706530225500\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Those who carefully observe these three key points \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":98,\"end\":149}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":98,\"end\":149,\"uuid\":\"43f73aef-5857-42bd-8109-ce525a609b28\"}},{\"type\":\"line\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Will enter the divine assemblies.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":149,\"end\":182}}],\"attrs\":{\"start\":149,\"end\":182,\"uuid\":\"ce2a6db8-41cc-4630-9794-94074109d4da\"}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"d25eccf3-ddea-4539-b684-be88e671f94c\",\"sort\":1407,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.52\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":137,\"uuid\":\"d25eccf3-ddea-4539-b684-be88e671f94c\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Therefore, regardless of the causes and conditions, one should refrain from \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":77}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":77,\"end\":82},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"adc9a9e5-a7a4-40a9-bd53-9d51e94c7d33\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and should not rejoice in lies told by others, either.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":82,\"end\":137}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"1da821a8-fc84-4831-b78f-479d6d9c8734\",\"sort\":1411,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.53\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":539,\"uuid\":\"1da821a8-fc84-4831-b78f-479d6d9c8734\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Nor should one seek out, take part in, or participate in conversations with liars, lest others will think that one is a liar oneself. Thus, if one befriends people who are fond of tainted activities, others will come to think of oneself as tainted as well. That is to say, one ought not keep negative company. Negative company leads to bondage in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":348}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":348,\"end\":364},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"b236c72d-9754-4c51-b7ea-feb5cc676aeb\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and birth in the realms of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":364,\"end\":392}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":392,\"end\":403},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"4e0b24e1-1143-4f25-83b6-3ab4b2ade481\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":403,\"end\":405}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirits\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":405,\"end\":421},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"bee81925-7216-44fc-8704-da1f914d88ac\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":421,\"end\":427}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animals\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":427,\"end\":434},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"f1b45352-a004-4258-a9b5-d8fb10208ac7\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Virtuous company, on the other hand, leads to supreme liberation. This is a brief explanation of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":434,\"end\":533}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":533,\"end\":538},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"d14ba178-4b04-4f93-bfd2-a04fb6ea2651\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":538,\"end\":539}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"0ebafbc8-1eeb-4388-8894-e227cc56f144\",\"sort\":1425,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.54\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":550,\"uuid\":\"0ebafbc8-1eeb-4388-8894-e227cc56f144\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"3bc24193-0ed4-47c3-8a22-cd8ef1c08a52\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":9}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":9,\"end\":22},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"8e8e46be-7d71-4475-8480-aaa745c1e245\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and what forms does it assume? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena perceive this either through knowledge derived from hearing or by seeing with the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":22,\"end\":198}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":198,\"end\":208},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"68d0f9f5-a099-42fb-91bb-ab43c2299583\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":208,\"end\":210}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":210,\"end\":223},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"a8a32643-855c-419a-8aa1-8e5ed5a0caec\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" occurs when words are spoken to sow discord among those who otherwise enjoyed harmonious relationships. There are two forms of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":223,\"end\":351}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":351,\"end\":364},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"696f2d50-c469-48e2-b17d-840611f8e2ab\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\": direct and indirect. That is to say, one might instruct someone to cause a rift among two people so that they become enemies or adversaries, or one might also seek to do so personally.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":364,\"end\":550}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"4c4ceebe-bfaa-47d4-866c-10b8b7141c61\",\"sort\":1435,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.55\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":890,\"uuid\":\"4c4ceebe-bfaa-47d4-866c-10b8b7141c61\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"80bacc90-9bcd-4589-84d7-b2228577abc2\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What then are \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":15}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":15,\"end\":26},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"c4f1aeae-7b1f-4765-b40f-789209146186\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and what forms do they assume? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena perceive this either through knowledge derived from hearing or by seeing with the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":26,\"end\":203}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":203,\"end\":213},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"a8a8ab2d-c73c-47e4-9eea-ffd7b34db7a9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":213,\"end\":215}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":215,\"end\":226},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"291c2cbc-6e69-40d0-9a39-f5a924ed3381\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" are harmful to oneself and others. They are the concordant cause of anger, and they are unattractive, ugly, and unpleasant to listen to. They involve desire, anger, and delusion, and they are engaged in by all infantile, ordinary individuals. They take numerous forms and involve numerous observations, causes, mental states, and types of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":226,\"end\":566}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ripening\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":566,\"end\":574},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e6c5ad9a-9509-4706-9d6f-5fad607030a7\",\"uuid\":\"b20a99b4-b90f-4a44-af0c-dc29e48b6f12\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", as well as numerous ways of destroying the joyful destinations. They make everyone unhappy and they cause and support anger in the world. They provoke destruction, breed distrust and unkindness, and emerge from a poisonous tongue. Thus, the stains of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":574,\"end\":827}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":827,\"end\":838},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"82a88701-ecdb-4433-bbac-9428c0f01bc4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" are to be avoided by all who practice \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":838,\"end\":877}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"pure conduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":877,\"end\":889},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7219540f-f47d-40cc-a2b8-cad5b3fe17da\",\"uuid\":\"a05400b8-2a4e-4835-a2b1-dce405021d60\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":889,\"end\":890}}]}]},{\"ty