will\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":15,\"end\":23},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6276adee-879f-4e8b-af6c-c11d910d5aaa\",\"uuid\":\"d0d177e7-27dd-45ad-9ba3-0535b4ae5b09\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":23,\"end\":29}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"wrong view\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":29,\"end\":39},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5b457f37-2050-4b7a-a1bd-a4844678591e\",\"uuid\":\"255c89a0-9c56-43d7-8395-4f8c8ac5cd0b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" belong to the path of unvirtuous mental acts. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":39,\"end\":86}}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":86,\"end\":892,\"uuid\":\"c7c01938-d77d-4d95-a79f-66dc667e57bd\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Among these, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":86,\"end\":100}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"covetousness\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":100,\"end\":112},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8c2659d2-1fca-40d2-bb49-a316cf575e54\",\"uuid\":\"c646315f-1c08-42d1-a8bc-bb7463504487\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is the state of being mentally and verbally obsessed with the substances and features of wealth procured by others, thinking, ‘This should be mine!’ \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":112,\"end\":262}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Covetousness\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":262,\"end\":274},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8c2659d2-1fca-40d2-bb49-a316cf575e54\",\"uuid\":\"70bf6e4f-a553-4c09-8446-7a3789e2b1d9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is that form of inappropriate mental engagement that is an impulsive reaction to, and craving for, the fine circumstances of others. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":274,\"end\":408}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Covetousness\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":408,\"end\":420},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8c2659d2-1fca-40d2-bb49-a316cf575e54\",\"uuid\":\"9b447a17-8983-4c81-9236-a05b7e1e08ec\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is an unvirtuous action, and its \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":420,\"end\":454}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ripening\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":454,\"end\":462},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e6c5ad9a-9509-4706-9d6f-5fad607030a7\",\"uuid\":\"bc521f11-6ee9-4c26-98bc-a8d82b76e129\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is unattractive, ugly, and unpleasant. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":462,\"end\":502}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Covetousness\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":502,\"end\":514},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8c2659d2-1fca-40d2-bb49-a316cf575e54\",\"uuid\":\"18d5f34e-6b36-41bc-9acc-107e0fbb58d0\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" fools restless and untrained, childish beings by creating a compulsive obsession with the fine circumstances of others. Thus, one seeks to obtain their fine circumstances, repeatedly and all-encompassingly, while wishing for and craving them to the extent that the very perception of such circumstances becomes painful. This is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":514,\"end\":843}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"covetousness\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":843,\"end\":855},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8c2659d2-1fca-40d2-bb49-a316cf575e54\",\"uuid\":\"1c441e22-ec20-4cca-b851-1b9d093498c1\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", a great stain among mental actions.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":855,\"end\":892}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"84998810-13a3-406a-9582-125c548729e0\",\"sort\":1634,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.75\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1110,\"uuid\":\"84998810-13a3-406a-9582-125c548729e0\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"ad6641a6-0581-4955-9d24-4f8b52da1275\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“How does the mental state of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":30}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ill will\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":30,\"end\":38},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6276adee-879f-4e8b-af6c-c11d910d5aaa\",\"uuid\":\"e46c7e1d-42c3-4205-9d92-af07ffcca541\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" constitute a negative course of action? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this either through knowledge derived from hearing or by means of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":38,\"end\":215}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":215,\"end\":225},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"966e2800-7a1e-464c-9bc6-49a29237aa2f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". They see how the illusory mental flaw of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":225,\"end\":268}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ill will\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":268,\"end\":276},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6276adee-879f-4e8b-af6c-c11d910d5aaa\",\"uuid\":\"7715d23a-f170-4f0c-a595-f5ac8a5651e7\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" may arise\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":276,\"end\":286},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"385121d9-44c7-4e96-a22c-9c2187863be3\",\"label\":\"21\",\"uuid\":\"026b038f-7efe-4398-8aeb-a78ee1dfa380\",\"start\":286,\"end\":286,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" when observing others, regardless of whether they are excellent or not. Thus, one might act as one pleases with regard to that illusion,\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":286,\"end\":423},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"6e0d3746-2a28-4178-9a4c-b8ed8f59cc80\",\"label\":\"22\",\"uuid\":\"1dbdea9b-0c59-47d6-acef-e0d25acbd963\",\"start\":423,\"end\":423,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and so sustain an extremely severe mental flaw. Such \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":423,\"end\":477}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ill will\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":477,\"end\":485},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6276adee-879f-4e8b-af6c-c11d910d5aaa\",\"uuid\":\"2bf9762f-b2db-444d-a705-44644e98c3c5\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" leads to the experience of life in hell. It is like hail to the crops of virtuous qualities and is antithetical to the eye of true \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":485,\"end\":617}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"insight\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":617,\"end\":624},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"dd19cf68-69ee-4f3b-bb5f-2c47fbe86706\",\"uuid\":\"045c0f47-393b-4897-8098-932e95e25bdf\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". This fire within the heart of darkness burns away spiritual discipline. It is a cause of ugliness and cuts through the supports for the Dharma. It is the enemy of both this world and the worlds to come. It destroys one-pointedness, combats love, and demolishes the noble one’s four truths of suffering, origin, path, and cessation. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":624,\"end\":958}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ill will\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":958,\"end\":966},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6276adee-879f-4e8b-af6c-c11d910d5aaa\",\"uuid\":\"d5a99607-88a0-4d97-9757-a87b156e44db\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is the supreme harbinger of life in hell. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":966,\"end\":1009}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ill will\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1009,\"end\":1017},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6276adee-879f-4e8b-af6c-c11d910d5aaa\",\"uuid\":\"7b25c7f9-1449-402d-9b00-4eb25861ff65\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is therefore abandoned by all holy beings, noble \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1017,\"end\":1067}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hearers\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1067,\"end\":1074},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5a90184b-4c5f-424b-8a34-4d859dc83b2f\",\"uuid\":\"cbdb74b2-157e-4c4e-88b8-4d0cc86b93d8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and people in pursuit of learning.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1074,\"end\":1110}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"4e61b104-e6b1-4922-9b31-d84d254067e1\",\"sort\":1658,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.76\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":681,\"uuid\":\"4e61b104-e6b1-4922-9b31-d84d254067e1\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"7c1056f8-4263-452d-958b-8ec53e7b4fe5\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What is the function of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":25}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"wrong view\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":25,\"end\":35},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5b457f37-2050-4b7a-a1bd-a4844678591e\",\"uuid\":\"fcd49d9f-720e-417a-87fc-fecb70e061d6\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", this darkness that grows in the hearts of beings in the form of negative beliefs that run counter to the sacred Dharma? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena perceive this either through knowledge derived from hearing or by seeing with the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":35,\"end\":301}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":301,\"end\":311},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"709648e7-caa4-4c46-b9b7-fca8db4a4942\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":311,\"end\":313}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Wrong view\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":313,\"end\":323},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5b457f37-2050-4b7a-a1bd-a4844678591e\",\"uuid\":\"5e8d96fc-b03d-4cb4-b0ff-ba467ea61675\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" has been present and has arisen since time without beginning. It is the cause of becoming a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":323,\"end\":416}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":416,\"end\":426},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"f82732f3-9f40-40a5-ac41-6fdbb4a054e9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":426,\"end\":430}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirit\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":430,\"end\":445},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"53924f0e-17c5-4ba2-afb9-add8ff66d95b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", or an \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":445,\"end\":453}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animal\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":453,\"end\":459},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"f5bd1c52-aeb4-4657-a906-060c6402dd70\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". It is pitch-black darkness. It is a fondness for negative beliefs. It is antithetical to the genuine path. It is like a weapon, fire, poison, and an abyss. It destroys all beings. It is a view that is wrong and mistaken.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":459,\"end\":681}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"3e566fae-765b-472b-8652-71fc3a18b92a\",\"sort\":1672,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.77\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":468,\"uuid\":\"3e566fae-765b-472b-8652-71fc3a18b92a\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“There are two kinds of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":24}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"wrong view\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":24,\"end\":34},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5b457f37-2050-4b7a-a1bd-a4844678591e\",\"uuid\":\"d92b2e9c-ef4d-442f-93be-b028089eb5d3\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\": those that accept the existence of conditions and those that deny karmic actions and results. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":34,\"end\":130}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To accept conditions\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":130,\"end\":150},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":130,\"end\":150,\"uuid\":\"3e564489-7e64-4ae2-af4c-a175aaaef669\",\"type\":\"span\",\"textStyle\":\"distinct\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is to claim that all happiness and suffering is the result of actions carried out by oneself. \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":150,\"end\":245}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"To deny karmic actions and results\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":245,\"end\":279},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"italic\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":245,\"end\":279,\"uuid\":\"bb244636-1069-4ede-a234-bccb6da6cd15\",\"type\":\"span\",\"textStyle\":\"distinct\"}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is to deny the relevance of generosity, and so forth. Thus, as the basis of all ten unvirtuous actions, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":279,\"end\":384}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"wrong view\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":384,\"end\":394},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5b457f37-2050-4b7a-a1bd-a4844678591e\",\"uuid\":\"3b6736ca-786f-42b6-87cd-c749790aa383\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" functions as the fundamental destroyer of all meaningful objectives. [B2]\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":394,\"end\":468}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"be8502aa-5ab8-4319-ad63-49c87464b887\",\"sort\":1685,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.78\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1004,\"uuid\":\"be8502aa-5ab8-4319-ad63-49c87464b887\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"1ab3d716-f015-4731-931f-68d73ae36bea\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Having turned away from the path of these ten unvirtuous actions, how does one instead engage in defiled or undefiled acts? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this either through knowledge derived from hearing or by means of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":261}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":261,\"end\":271},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"8d3d97c2-732c-4502-a1a5-26b93bfda9f4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Unvirtuous actions lead to bondage in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":271,\"end\":311}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":311,\"end\":327},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"2e1a0652-7652-4651-b44f-4459a8120ed2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and the exhaustion of Dharma. Virtue, on the other hand, is what causes liberation. Giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":327,\"end\":422}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":422,\"end\":429},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"19bc47f7-eb4d-48e2-8b7e-27164b8244df\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", one gives freedom from fear to all the beings in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":429,\"end\":480}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":480,\"end\":496},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"adacaba6-45bb-4887-8163-24439fb92182\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". One will be praised in the present life, have a beautiful countenance, enjoy bright \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":496,\"end\":582}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"faculties\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":582,\"end\":591},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"3fa3f050-4af9-405f-9d21-f34808303e7b\",\"uuid\":\"6b55f191-680a-45dd-be60-350ff2a21397\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and carry out acts that engender longevity. Those who day and night protect even harmful creatures such as \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":591,\"end\":700}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"rākṣasas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":700,\"end\":708},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b21f414a-955c-4574-a5e2-4dfc51ccfb88\",\"uuid\":\"0b3e6257-028c-4538-b74a-af3d7a21f787\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":708,\"end\":710}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"piśācas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":710,\"end\":717},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"02559a9d-b6dd-4119-bc9a-77e18e40ec84\",\"uuid\":\"dd95c9ec-0e9d-46ea-8323-3ff863d927e7\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", or \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":717,\"end\":722}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"kumbhāṇḍas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":722,\"end\":732},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"1e2966da-80fb-4f8b-96c9-0d1c17655cda\",\"uuid\":\"529a80e0-2081-4635-adb1-906c3ed5860a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" of different kinds will thereafter be protected by the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":732,\"end\":788}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"gods\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":788,\"end\":792},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"2a0d9d5c-75a8-4156-965d-87dbb547e9ca\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and when they separate from their bodies, they will be born in the joyful divine realms. If you want to experience the effect of such \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":792,\"end\":928}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"ripening\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":928,\"end\":936},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e6c5ad9a-9509-4706-9d6f-5fad607030a7\",\"uuid\":\"8d7ce4b6-eb84-46df-aebc-9abb9537fd60\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", then know that such experience is proportionate to your diligence.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":936,\"end\":1004}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"888d2ff8-56f5-4261-b78f-a5e602fbe3b9\",\"sort\":1707,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.79\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":601,\"uuid\":\"888d2ff8-56f5-4261-b78f-a5e602fbe3b9\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“If one wishes to experience the minor, intermediate, or great paths of awakening, then this is how they follow. Dedication toward the awakening of a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":150}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hearer\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":150,\"end\":156},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5a90184b-4c5f-424b-8a34-4d859dc83b2f\",\"uuid\":\"8fec7391-e3b3-494a-a1e9-caeb4c03bc1b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will turn one into a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":156,\"end\":178}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"worthy one\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":178,\"end\":188},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"69eec99c-d322-425f-bc83-85bb4b1e65ae\",\"uuid\":\"538cc7a6-1c39-4cfd-ba69-189fd910e7a3\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and one will go completely beyond suffering. Dedication toward intermediate awakening will make one a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":188,\"end\":291}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"solitary buddha\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":291,\"end\":306},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c1a27d3a-9591-4376-8678-41d3848a2125\",\"uuid\":\"6ae8eafb-0f2a-4aa5-8f46-9add9706fd6f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". If one’s dedication is toward unsurpassable and perfect awakening, one will become a perfect buddha. Endowed with knowledge and its support, one will become a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":306,\"end\":467}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"well-gone one\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":467,\"end\":480},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5763e542-6c29-456b-b615-8af8550f1dfc\",\"uuid\":\"a8543860-4cff-4bbf-b4b5-dde8aac19083\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", a knower of the world, a steersman who tames beings, an unexcelled one, a teacher of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":480,\"end\":567}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"gods\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":567,\"end\":571},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"3bbd778b-7087-4b6c-8c64-ddbfcfb9244d\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and humans, a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":571,\"end\":586}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"blessed\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":586,\"end\":593},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"096407a8-2631-4818-90b7-90d522c2f84b\",\"uuid\":\"92376577-af1f-41bc-a1be-bfa427bc338a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" buddha.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":593,\"end\":601}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"5dbf4b4f-9a29-4e09-98bb-ca960d772201\",\"sort\":1723,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.80\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1291,\"uuid\":\"5dbf4b4f-9a29-4e09-98bb-ca960d772201\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Life is the root of all qualities. Hence, protecting life is a gift that grants all forms of happiness. Among all forms of generosity, the mental state of wishing to give life is supreme. Among all forms of discipline, the discipline of giving life is the supreme way to gain rebirth in the higher realms. If the practice of such discipline is dedicated toward the enjoyment of objects that serve as causes of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":411}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"affliction\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":411,\"end\":421},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9a4b2555-d9c2-41b4-a5c0-2a8a0a115fa5\",\"uuid\":\"55865a96-dc4d-4b8c-a321-f5ff29b45e41\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and craving, then one will become \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":421,\"end\":456}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Brahmā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":456,\"end\":462},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e4d3cd20-fd11-455c-844e-c5bb18b89e36\",\"uuid\":\"39feaa02-15cb-4de6-a125-a8d29f6876b8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":462,\"end\":464}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Māra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":464,\"end\":468},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be33ec74-6b07-494d-b35c-c7fde200b8ac\",\"uuid\":\"6cd00a82-1734-4a87-a138-75bfddea9a3f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", or \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":468,\"end\":473}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Śakra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":473,\"end\":478},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c46473a9-c71c-4bc8-afb8-4c7b3d3f7bdb\",\"uuid\":\"64b91960-f413-4616-b988-6a19f605063f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". If it is dedicated to becoming a great human being, then one will become a universal monarch, possessing the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":478,\"end\":589}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"seven treasures\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":589,\"end\":604},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2a14dc53-a31c-4b0a-99d8-368aae405a5a\",\"uuid\":\"6f1a0920-d177-43bd-9cd5-d17978d25fef\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and ruling the four continents. If it is dedicated to becoming a great \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":604,\"end\":676}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"asura\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":676,\"end\":681},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5f1024e5-d735-4094-89c8-9a8baec55fd2\",\"uuid\":\"97ccf62a-d14c-40c8-925c-9f0d2168d0b3\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", one will rule the realm of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":681,\"end\":714}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"asuras\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":714,\"end\":720},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"5f1024e5-d735-4094-89c8-9a8baec55fd2\",\"uuid\":\"3c7b4689-bd49-4976-997d-a78fbf84ef05\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". If it is dedicated to becoming a great \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":720,\"end\":761}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"yakṣa\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":761,\"end\":766},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d3bfc42-ac48-41d3-b11a-e2ae12b0ad5c\",\"uuid\":\"a9b3cb90-4bae-46e5-a540-7c3b620b0c16\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" one will rule the realm of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":766,\"end\":798}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"yakṣas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":798,\"end\":804},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d3bfc42-ac48-41d3-b11a-e2ae12b0ad5c\",\"uuid\":\"2ba17114-63dc-4158-9d22-147d58146153\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". This great compassion is the seed of the sacred Dharma. It is a protection against \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":804,\"end\":889}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":889,\"end\":905},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"caee6da3-461d-4057-85b5-afb240e2dfb4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and a lamp for those who are lost in the darkness of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":905,\"end\":959}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":959,\"end\":975},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"d7190638-6d18-4e3a-aa49-5b07f980ab7b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Such is the practice of refraining from \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":975,\"end\":1017}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1017,\"end\":1024},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"f7d5dc44-c4b7-471e-8e81-1762a3ef8e54\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". By giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1024,\"end\":1039}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1039,\"end\":1046},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"f669dde6-14f2-4004-9f09-08ba20ae2cb5\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" one cultivates love and becomes a compassionate being. Deciding to refrain from \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1046,\"end\":1127}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1127,\"end\":1134},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"394a2cc9-398e-4d0e-8da7-9e30bb205995\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" brings purity and joy. When one is unable to actually save others, one should remain impartial. This will make one’s mind rest in the four \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1134,\"end\":1274}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"abodes of Brahmā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1274,\"end\":1290},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"6684be0d-4a7a-4862-b04b-4160d4aeae60\",\"uuid\":\"89c1fd68-ac56-4019-8464-5387e3aabe36\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1290,\"end\":1291}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"c2da7bcc-654d-4354-807f-ef8b39dc9480\",\"sort\":1755,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.81\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1160,\"uuid\":\"c2da7bcc-654d-4354-807f-ef8b39dc9480\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“In essence, the roots of virtue that ensue from having given up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":65}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":65,\"end\":72},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"a70f0dfb-50e2-4aa3-b21c-850b2828edd2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" are inconceivable because they accomplish whatever aim one may dedicate them to in whatever applicable way. As an analogy, when an expert goldsmith works with fine gold, he can turn it into anything he wants: ornaments, vases, human figures, or buddha figures. Similarly, someone who guards against \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":72,\"end\":372}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":372,\"end\":379},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"e178cfab-81e6-4f54-9aff-0bb311606c5a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and maintains that practice unerringly without violating it may accomplish whatever aim he or she is dedicated to in whatever applicable way. Thus, those who give up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":379,\"end\":546}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":546,\"end\":553},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"de19cdba-3729-4ef1-9b97-fd74c254cf0f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" are close to the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":553,\"end\":571}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"transcendence of suffering\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":571,\"end\":597},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ac32bc5b-668a-4237-964c-e794eb68dfc9\",\"uuid\":\"86b64425-6320-4c56-ab62-387b98d0087e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". They will enjoy the company of spiritual teachers and possess the fortune of benefiting themselves and others. They are a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":597,\"end\":721}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"field of merit\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":721,\"end\":735},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e843c74a-1afe-4437-b242-1d0fe966c6d0\",\"uuid\":\"6e1d776d-7622-4e14-b0c5-852a6e76741a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" for \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":735,\"end\":740}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell beings\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":740,\"end\":751},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"3cee9639-80da-40a1-85fa-35deece8b84f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":751,\"end\":753}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"animals\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":753,\"end\":760},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"49e78f8f-4702-4a65-846b-a7e3bc5ee165\",\"uuid\":\"5d5f958c-e31c-4320-a97c-30fd3248dde8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":760,\"end\":766}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"starving spirits\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":766,\"end\":782},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"84f73a9d-4c5c-400b-a557-976d1d6779b3\",\"uuid\":\"78e4aecd-e782-4a6b-95b6-09dcf80f5cb9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Within \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":782,\"end\":791}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"cyclic existence\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":791,\"end\":807},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7f9b4269-ecf7-4226-9cbd-3ff52a609edb\",\"uuid\":\"53fae0f0-4a4d-4540-86a5-dd272bf46a36\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" they possess and follow the Dharma. They will accomplish the ideals of those who possess the Dharma and also become stable in this accomplishment. They are not frightened or oppressed by rulers, robbers, water, or fire. Rather, they find joy within. They are seen as unassailable by other peers who possess the Dharma. Thus, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":807,\"end\":1133}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"killing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1133,\"end\":1140},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"765a595f-12c6-4f20-9dfc-8c1d9d2bb9b2\",\"uuid\":\"0efc2d04-a67f-459b-a8bc-73c4e0e0c1d2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" should be given up.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1140,\"end\":1160}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"66be46f9-b5d1-4f95-964b-ed14c6f9d707\",\"sort\":1779,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.82\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1313,\"uuid\":\"66be46f9-b5d1-4f95-964b-ed14c6f9d707\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"b290d472-50f5-48f1-87c3-8f5734f221df\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What goodness comes of refraining from \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":40}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":40,\"end\":48},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"2f4e07ff-64e9-4847-b1f8-7d7f55c689e6\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this by means of knowledge derived from hearing or through the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":48,\"end\":179}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":179,\"end\":189},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"85e89eb7-5b45-49fe-b919-8c2551c9554f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". By giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":189,\"end\":204}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"stealing\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":204,\"end\":212},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9ad933f8-ddbc-4390-be33-dfde30d736b8\",\"uuid\":\"a117a9c1-7d20-4599-9686-da92164ec5e5\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" one will escape the net of great avarice for objects owned by others. One will find relief in the present life. Taken into confidence by kings and ministers, as well as by courts, households, noble families, monastic congregations, and priestly gatherings, one will be regarded as delightful, dear, attractive, and authoritative. The enjoyments of such a person will be constant. And without bringing harm to others, one will have no fear of rulers, water, robbers, or fire. Unanticipated, such enjoyments will arise spontaneously. Once these have arisen, one will be a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":212,\"end\":783}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"field of merit\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":783,\"end\":797},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e843c74a-1afe-4437-b242-1d0fe966c6d0\",\"uuid\":\"2469bfea-6f23-40f8-ae1d-741d914d9ff8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", embody discipline, embark upon a good path, and develop close ties with worldly beings. Furthermore, when separating from the body one will be born in the joyful divine realms. If the merit of this is dedicated by means of the path of deliverance, one will find deliverance and, in the same way as before, become a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":797,\"end\":1114}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Brahmā\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1114,\"end\":1120},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e4d3cd20-fd11-455c-844e-c5bb18b89e36\",\"uuid\":\"94ce9eaf-30d1-4521-bbcd-6a1a60a3c46e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1120,\"end\":1122}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Māra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1122,\"end\":1126},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"be33ec74-6b07-494d-b35c-c7fde200b8ac\",\"uuid\":\"46b83751-cb4b-44e6-b7ab-02c9625f2069\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1126,\"end\":1128}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Śakra\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1128,\"end\":1133},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c46473a9-c71c-4bc8-afb8-4c7b3d3f7bdb\",\"uuid\":\"1077029c-31a9-4ccd-a6c4-0f92d2114fb8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", or a universal monarch who rules the four continents and possesses the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1133,\"end\":1206}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"seven treasures\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1206,\"end\":1221},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"2a14dc53-a31c-4b0a-99d8-368aae405a5a\",\"uuid\":\"c41f54df-5088-4c19-9a3c-ca376474df9f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Likewise, those who delight in discipline will attain their respective forms of awakening.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1221,\"end\":1313}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"41a8deb5-ad78-400f-ae11-7eef15a94f1e\",\"sort\":1799,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.83\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":780,\"uuid\":\"41a8deb5-ad78-400f-ae11-7eef15a94f1e\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"d2e89677-add6-48bb-a5e0-c9aee25b98bf\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“What are the effects of giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":35}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":35,\"end\":52},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"8a5ba3ea-cb4b-469a-b58f-8b065cd12ea0\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this by means of knowledge derived from hearing or through the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":52,\"end\":183}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":183,\"end\":193},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"4efab5bb-45d8-4e4e-84ce-16d2fb0b5d39\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":193,\"end\":205}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":205,\"end\":222},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"97d68599-a861-4807-9346-bd111aca888b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" leads to good deeds and virtuous action. One will be praised and trusted in the present life. One will not feel nervous around women. Kings and ministers will take one into their confidence. One’s spouse will never be stolen by someone else, but always act with respect and in accordance with one’s own intentions. Even in hard times there will not be any mockery, disrespect, or inclination to attack one another. One’s spouse will not be blamed by anyone and she will act like a mother or sister to the whole world, being free from any anger at the world.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":222,\"end\":780}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"f44498fc-6f14-4f39-9664-a24f2dff53d1\",\"sort\":1809,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.84\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":842,\"uuid\":\"f44498fc-6f14-4f39-9664-a24f2dff53d1\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“As before, when separating from one’s body, one will take birth within the joyful divine realms. When later the time has come to die in that \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":142}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"god\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":142,\"end\":145},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"5787cc2d-9a91-446c-b3a7-c7d4afa518a8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" realm, one will be reborn as another \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":145,\"end\":183}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"god\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":183,\"end\":186},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"f8ac8308-ee08-4227-bb2d-96b2a2fb5b59\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" there. If, on the other hand, one has engaged in \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":186,\"end\":236}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":236,\"end\":253},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"a2fbc61b-42a1-49f4-bd00-5fdab7947473\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", another \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":253,\"end\":263}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"god\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":263,\"end\":266},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"eca545ed-6c6b-49a9-bed8-0ddcd9ecf65b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will, while one is still alive in that realm, be born among the divine maidens and become visible to them. The divine maidens will then jest, smile, and have fun with that \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":266,\"end\":439}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"god\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":439,\"end\":442},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"d6c032f8-8cf0-4892-881f-526d69d85823\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Later, when one’s wife sees one is dying, she will abandon one to be with that other \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":442,\"end\":529}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"god\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":529,\"end\":532},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"3a7f1eb5-8493-476f-bc53-2c8972c713e9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Thus, caught by the shackles of envy, one will take birth as a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":532,\"end\":597}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"hell being\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":597,\"end\":607},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"75490385-7dc4-45eb-a8ee-660e965e39a8\",\"uuid\":\"e63e2155-98bb-4f35-9f8b-88ffd50f2d79\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Resorting to, becoming habituated to, and increasing acts of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":607,\"end\":670}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":670,\"end\":687},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"0d6fafef-d379-44a5-b9ad-f4befb87fbeb\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is a great obstacle. Therefore, giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":687,\"end\":730}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"sexual misconduct\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":730,\"end\":747},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9db826d-bfc2-49ef-a9b0-bbe70bf16d26\",\"uuid\":\"2bc00c42-0ad1-4dd4-a5a2-4e9448dfab02\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" will allow one to follow the great path of virtue and gain the fortune to transcend suffering.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":747,\"end\":842}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"876bfe68-6c13-4c41-aed6-5ee555ba7346\",\"sort\":1829,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.85\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1230,\"uuid\":\"876bfe68-6c13-4c41-aed6-5ee555ba7346\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"72e4f697-e488-4a62-a9b6-68b9f8010bb1\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“By giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":14}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":14,\"end\":19},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"bbd88c7b-a488-4614-b069-b7a7aedf3309\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", which is incompatible with all virtuous inclinations, one upholds highly virtuous inclination. What, then, are the ripened effects of this in this present life? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this by means of knowledge derived from hearing or through the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":19,\"end\":311}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":311,\"end\":321},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"4fb97684-e438-49b1-9093-77af163156cb\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". By giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":321,\"end\":336}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"lying\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":336,\"end\":341},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9d9ddb6c-fc25-472b-8d22-bd6defd1b514\",\"uuid\":\"31bfe3f5-8f8c-4753-b561-fe8bc4b823a0\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" one will be trusted even by people who have never seen or heard of oneself. Should one be lacking in terms of wealth, all one’s wishes will be fulfilled by both the people and the king. Like the moon that shines brightly in the midst of the other planets and celestial bodies, those who speak the truth will shine brightly amid all worldly people. Among all jewels, the great jewel of the truth is supreme and sublime. Among all that liberates us from all cycles of existence, the liberator of the truth is particularly exalted. Among all that turns us away from the lower realms, the repellent of the truth is supreme. Truth is the lamp of all lamps and the guide of all guides. Among all forms of substance, it is the substance of truth that removes the sickness of others. Truth is the force among all forces, the protector among all protectors, and the most exalted among all friends.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":341,\"end\":1230}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"c5ae9e8e-b14b-4eb9-a738-eb164f8094be\",\"sort\":1839,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.86\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":967,\"uuid\":\"c5ae9e8e-b14b-4eb9-a738-eb164f8094be\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Those who possess the wealth of truth will never experience the poverty of falling into the lower realms. Instead, they will be close to the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":141}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"gods\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":141,\"end\":145},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"4f3f65c8-d161-4ae3-8f87-9cb349170888\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Wherever such people are born they will take birth in a fine family and have an excellent physique. Everyone will find them appealing, delightful, attractive, and trustworthy. Such people will be imperceptible to \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":145,\"end\":360}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"rākṣasas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":360,\"end\":368},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b21f414a-955c-4574-a5e2-4dfc51ccfb88\",\"uuid\":\"6e63d1dc-07ae-41a1-9122-daa23cbe7f83\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" and \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":368,\"end\":373}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"piśācas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":373,\"end\":380},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"02559a9d-b6dd-4119-bc9a-77e18e40ec84\",\"uuid\":\"512bf0d2-4db4-4690-af29-a253ae07a008\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and invulnerable to their harm. Whenever such people travel they will find plentiful and excellent lodging and medical treatment. Anything they may wish for will be fulfilled. Such people will experience supreme human happiness and, when the time of their death comes, they will separate from their bodies only to be born in the joyous divine realms, where they will enjoy extremely long lives, tremendous miraculous powers, and an exceedingly exalted status. Just as before, if one dedicates this in a pure and undefiled manner, it will bring the liberation of transcending suffering.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":380,\"end\":967}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"cdcc7259-e2c8-4ef3-8e23-b7b7008319de\",\"sort\":1847,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.87\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1495,\"uuid\":\"cdcc7259-e2c8-4ef3-8e23-b7b7008319de\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"c45664e9-dfad-49ed-988e-e923d23087a9\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“As one practices virtuous actions, what are the effects of giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":70}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":70,\"end\":83},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"e3dd44ba-d79f-46b1-a413-1b07fa80fd1d\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", as they ripen in this life and beyond? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this by means of knowledge derived from hearing or through the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":83,\"end\":253}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":253,\"end\":263},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"a94b92ca-1970-429e-beb7-6d879ba17cf9\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". The ripened effect that is experienced in this life due to giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":263,\"end\":334}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":334,\"end\":347},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"76344bf2-a855-4c6f-8fe7-bd1510cf1575\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is to have steadfast friends, acquaintances, relatives, spouses, male servants, female servants, workers, and employees. One will not be led along by others, and none among one’s friends, the members of the royal court, or discordant relatives will be able to create any factions. Should one lose one’s wealth, one will not become destitute. Neither will one suffer any loss when encountering famine, isolated places, mountains, precipices, or temporary adversities. Should one criticize others, one will not be persecuted. At the royal court one will prevail, and one will not have any fear of water, weapons, or animosity. Such are the qualities associated with giving up the great stain that is \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":347,\"end\":1046}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1046,\"end\":1059},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"35caa778-1176-4631-92b5-e61d12c5f183\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Having died and separated from the body, one will be born in the joyful and divine higher realms. There great gatherings of affectionate goddesses of similar ilk will please one with flower garlands, colored powders, perfumes, and jewelry. Just as before, if one’s relinquishment of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1059,\"end\":1344}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divisive talk\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1344,\"end\":1357},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"12b408c6-c323-4da1-b5b2-76d8f03e4237\",\"uuid\":\"b265fce7-1a5a-4626-9668-afdbe2659db2\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is dedicated in a pure and undefiled manner, one will achieve the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1357,\"end\":1424}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"transcendence of suffering\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1424,\"end\":1450},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ac32bc5b-668a-4237-964c-e794eb68dfc9\",\"uuid\":\"ee612b69-37e4-49ed-a592-e5245cbecf28\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" through the path of undefiled \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1450,\"end\":1481}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"concentration\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1481,\"end\":1494},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"28497d42-519a-4fae-9a73-8c5c4f1fd44e\",\"uuid\":\"53013a33-430b-43a7-92c3-bd67a50759d4\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1494,\"end\":1495}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"da22faec-716b-4c43-8698-8ad82c068ff0\",\"sort\":1865,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"1.88\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":1362,\"uuid\":\"da22faec-716b-4c43-8698-8ad82c068ff0\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"2eff2d40-ff8a-4545-b942-2998ca7a3af5\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"“Speaking \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":10}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":10,\"end\":21},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"c956840e-9433-4dfa-bb83-4c154008e82a\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is an unvirtuous action that saddens the entire world. What are the effects that ripen by giving up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":21,\"end\":122}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":122,\"end\":133},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"a0bc73c5-69f2-4139-86c4-8fdf94335871\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"? Spiritual practitioners who carefully observe inner phenomena see this by means of knowledge derived from hearing or through the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":133,\"end\":264}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"divine eye\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":264,\"end\":274},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"bfe4d6ca-3e0f-4dde-a8bb-7c5149937f8b\",\"uuid\":\"e4f43496-bb97-4fe7-80c1-5dffd92e0815\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". Those who give up \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":274,\"end\":294}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"harsh words\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":294,\"end\":305},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"ec8f7f40-6c08-41c1-abc2-6cce205065e8\",\"uuid\":\"36851883-3a64-4b6f-b1fa-74a84f0b2cc8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" come to witness what is virtuous. Such people are naturally honest and a source of comfort. They are esteemed by the whole world. They speak gently and pleasantly, while refraining from harming anyone and bringing everyone comfort. When such people are seen in the distance, everyone wants to approach them. Such people have many friends, and even if they lack material wealth, everyone will act like servants toward them. Even if they should happen to disturb anyone, others will not abandon them. All their objectives will be accomplished without any trouble. Such people will never have to fear animosity, the authorities, water, fire, or weapons. When they later separate from their bodies, they will take birth among the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":305,\"end\":1032}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"gods\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1032,\"end\":1036},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"001a0a5f-1d64-4686-98cb-d50f70cca517\",\"uuid\":\"f7b16a93-cf70-4c8e-a33d-79d8602e5942\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" in the joyful and divine higher realms. Even then, their words will be gentle, beneficial, and delightful, and they will possess great miracles and great powers. As before, if this is dedicated in an undefiled manner toward the blissful abode of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1036,\"end\":1287}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"concentration\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1287,\"end\":1300},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"28497d42-519a-4fae-9a73-8c5c4f1fd44e\",\"uuid\":\"9b147f7d-d019-4850-a391-d2135f47acda\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" of deliverance, one will attain the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1300,\"end\":1337}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"three kinds of awakening\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1337,\"end\":1361},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"d74740fc-80b1-4f01-b5fe-d0fa8d7a8e59\",\"uuid\":\"c22d6956-8883-4828-836c-0c057c262858\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1361,\"end\":1362}}]}]}]}]\n"])</script><div hidden id="S:2"><div dir="ltr" data-orientation="horizontal" data-slot="tabs" class="flex flex-col gap-2 px-12 w-full"><div class="sticky top-0.75 -mt-28 z-10 w-full over